Instead this library might be a better fit: https://github.com/deanWombourne/node-diawi

Especially since it already has a default polling time of 2 seconds:
```js
const POLL_INTERVAL = 2;
const DEBUG = false;

const sleep = (seconds) => {
  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
    setTimeout(resolve, (seconds * 1000));
  });
};
```
